title: Girl Group Discusses Relationship Red Flags + Dave Ramsey Answers The Show's Money Questions

description:
Is it a red flag if your family doesn't like your significant other? The Girl Group weighs in. Also, Dave Ramsey stops by the studio and answers the show's money questions including how much Producer Raymundo should spend on an engagement ring.
